{"slide_id": "20d95200c4abf876205b85c17f55b2d3-FAIR_and_Open_D__s4__G6_MARGIN_VIOLATION", "width": 1280, "height": 720, "elements": [{"element_id": "shp110", "type": "body", "bbox": {"x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "width": 1280.0, "height": 117.03}, "text": "Open Data Methods", "style": {"font_size_pt": 44.0}, "z": 0, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp111", "type": "body", "bbox": {"x": 1008.71, "y": 697.38, "width": 274.29, "height": 22.62}, "text": "Icons made by https://www.flaticon.com/authors/eucalyp", "style": {"font_size_pt": 8.0}, "z": 1, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp112", "type": "image", "bbox": {"x": 27.18, "y": 132.12, "width": 188.85, "height": 188.85}, "text": "", "style": {}, "z": 2, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp113", "type": "body", "bbox": {"x": 19.39, "y": 331.96, "width": 301.58, "height": 155.1}, "text": "Anonymisation:\nThe information that could identify an individual is randomly altered or stripped out.", "style": {"font_size_pt": 18.0}, "z": 3, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp114", "type": "image", "bbox": {"x": 401.44, "y": 197.14, "width": 212.37, "height": 212.37}, "text": "", "style": {}, "z": 4, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp115", "type": "body", "bbox": {"x": 751.85, "y": 169.71, "width": 513.72, "height": 416.83}, "text": "This tool is still in a beta version but provides a centralised method for anonymisation through a web interface by simply uploading your data files using drag and drop and it will then produce your desired anonymised data.\n\nIt is part of a suite of tools that are part of Open AIRE and the European Open Science Cloud (EOSC) which provide the tools for the workflow through the data lifecycle. Many commercial options exist too but anonymisation should also be possible through rigorous application of a workflow that applies established checks and balances.", "style": {"font_size_pt": 18.0}, "z": 5, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp116", "type": "body", "bbox": {"x": 320.97, "y": 427.93, "width": 389.81, "height": 140.24}, "text": "There are many tools available for anonymisation, but one that has been developed through the OpenAIRE is Amnesia.", "style": {"font_size_pt": 16.0, "color": "#595959"}, "z": 6, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp117", "type": "shape", "bbox": {"x": 700.39, "y": 575.89, "width": 151.01, "height": 88.24}, "text": "", "style": {}, "z": 7, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp118", "type": "image", "bbox": {"x": 924.94, "y": 610.34, "width": 155.06, "height": 43.74}, "text": "", "style": {}, "z": 8, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp119", "type": "shape", "bbox": {"x": 912.48, "y": 596.36, "width": 300.61, "height": 70.24}, "text": "", "style": {}, "z": 9, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp120", "type": "body", "bbox": {"x": 1092.45, "y": 612.08, "width": 120.64, "height": 42.01}, "text": "https://www.eosc-hub.eu/services", "style": {"font_size_pt": 10.0}, "z": 10, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp121", "type": "shape", "bbox": {"x": 369.24, "y": 612.68, "width": 300.61, "height": 72.81}, "text": "", "style": {}, "z": 11, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp122", "type": "body", "bbox": {"x": 541.84, "y": 628.4, "width": 128.0, "height": 42.01}, "text": "http://catalogue.openaire.eu/search", "style": {"font_size_pt": 10.0}, "z": 12, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp123", "type": "image", "bbox": {"x": 392.51, "y": 624.87, "width": 136.88, "height": 48.86}, "text": "", "style": {}, "z": 13, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}], "metadata": {"scene": "full_proposal", "source": "zenodo10k"}}